ZILOKHU zenyukile izibalo zabahaqwa yiCovid-19 kuleli nababulawa yileli gciwane. Izibalo zakamuva ezikhishwe wuMnyango wezeMpilo kuleli, zikhomba ukuthi emahoreni angu-24 abahaqwe yileli gciwane bangu-1 129, okuholele ekutheni izibalo zabahaqwe yigciwane zenyukele ku-1 597 724. Izifundazwe ezihamba phambili ngezibalo zabahaqwe yigciwane, yiGauteng enabantu abangu-428 717, Eastern Cape enabangu-196 307,  Western Cape ngabangu-288 299 neKwaZulu-Natal enabantu abangu-337 397. UMnyango wezeMpilo KwaZulu-Natal, ekhasini lawo leFacebook uthe emahoreni angu-24 bangu-64 abahaqwe yigciwane. Uthe lesi sifundazwe singesesine kwezihamba phambili ngezibalo eseziqale ukwenyuka zabahaqwe yigciwane, iGauteng ihamba phambili ngezibalo ezenyukayo. Bangu-54 825 ababulelwe yigciwane kuleli. Abashone esikhathi esingamahora angu-24 bangu-60. Ukwenyuka kwezibalo zabahaqwa yigciwane kuholele ekutheni abantu babe nengebhe, bazibuze ukuthi ngabe sesingenile yini isiqubu sesithathu sokuhlasela kwaleli gciwane. Abanye benze isiphakamiso sokuthi kuqiniswe imithetho elawula imingcele namachwepha. INhlangano yezeMpilo eMhlabeni, iWorld Health Organisation (WHO), yenze isiphakamiso sokuthi kulawulwe ukungena kwezivakashi emazweni ehlukene. Ithe akumele imingcele namachweba kuvalwe ngoba lokho kuzophazamisa ezomnotho. Kodwa amanye amazwe ayazinqabela izivakashi ezivela emazweni akholwa wukuthi anengozi kakhulu. Izivakashi eziphuma kuleli kazivumelekile e-USA. Izivakashi ezisatshwa kakhulu ngeziphuma e-India. UDkt Zweli Mkhize onguNgqongqoshe wezeMpilo kuleli, uthe kawekho amabhanoyi asuka e-India eza kuleli, izivakashi eziphuma khona ziyaxhuma. Ngenxa yalokho kubekwe imigomo emisha yokuthi izivakashi kumele zihlolwe. Uma kutholakala ukuthi zineCovid-19 zigonqe. 